npc/arif: This is the last stretch before the core. Think of it as a test.
npc/arif: Everything you've faced is gathered here — the jumps, the enemies, the traps — plus a few new footholds that won't hold still, or won't hold at all.
npc/arif: Some platforms move. Some drop the instant you trust them — like every "sure thing" this place ever sold you. Watch them, learn them, keep moving.
npc/arif: Prove you can make it through on your own. What waits at the end will not go easy on you.
